layout: post
title: Strawberry Chocolate Orange Smoothie
---

![Strawberry Chocolate Orange Smoothie](/images/strawberry_chocolate_orange_smoothie.jpg)

This delicious smoothie tastes like a Terry's Chocolate Orange, except instead of being high and sugar and calories, it's high in protein and nutrients! It's makes for a satisfying breakfast, snack, or dessert. Use it to conqour cravings and up your protein and vegetable intake. 

The recipe can be done in a few different ways. It also tastes with a banana added in. The measurements do not need to be exact, you can estimate. 

## Ingridents 
- 2 handfulls of spinach
- 3 big spoonfulls of plain Greek yogurt
- 3-4 scoops of chocolate protein powder
- 1-2 mandarins/celmintines/oranges 
- 6-10 strawberries 
- 1 spoonful of orange marmalade
- Orange juice 
- Stevia to taste 
